name: You Can Dance Anywhere! Swiss Alps Print for kids
description:
In 2012, a Mouse and Elephant danced their way around the globe! No one could stop them..... and why would they want to?  This duo is pretty adorable. Meet Bigzi and Floyd! They are best of friends, and they do absolutely everything together. 

This was the first print created for the series, "You Can Dance Anywhere" , and features our chirpy couple dancing in a meadow in the Swiss Alps! I can smell the fresh mountain air from here, can you?

Features:

- Hand drawn and colored, with only minimal digital touch-ups. Print is carefully made from the original.
- Printed on FSC approved, matte card stock paper. 
- Includes an 11" x 14" white mat, for easy framing. Also fits in to a variety of IKEA & standard frames.
- Signed by both artists in pencil
- Made and printed locally in Vancouver, BC 
- Ships with a clear protective sleeve in a flat-back cardboard mailing envelope, within 2 days of purchase.

name: "Everyday Dragon" Canvas Print for Kids - Limited Edition 30
description:
Have you ever wondered what Dragons do when they're not guarding castles and protecting princesses from evildoers? 

Well, we can show you with Pickle Punch's first limited edition Giclée print on canvas.  What better way to introduce ourselves than with a bunch of quirky and curious dragons!

Features:

- Printed on 100% cotton canvas 
- Hand drawn & colored with some digital touch ups. Very limited prints made from the original artwork 
- Printed with UV Protected, 4 color inkjet technology, so you can display your print in a sunny spot if you choose. Easy to clean. 
- Signed and numbered by both artists. Includes Certificate of Authenticity. 
- Ready to hang! Comes with mounting hooks and wire, so all you have to do is pick the spot, and hammer in the nail
- Very limited to only 30! So once they're sold ,you won't see them again! (Unless you have one in your home of course)
- Made, printed and hand-stretched locally in Vancouver, BC
- Shipped in bubble wrap, corner protected, in a cardboard box

Come and give these lovely beastly dragons their forever-home. Get yours today before they’re all gone!
